        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 8. Caulleriella venefica Doner & Blake, 2006. A, Entire worm, coiled; B, anterior end, left lateral view; C, anterior end, left lateral view of another specimen; D, anterior end, ventral view; E, anterior end, frontal view; F, left lateral view of setigers 12–14, noto- and neuropodia with capillaries and hooks evident; G, two neuropodial hooks and one capillary; H, one neuropodial hook and one capillary; I, posterior end, left lateral view. SEMs from three specimens on stub from Georges Bank Sta. 5-28, Cruise M10, Rep. 4, coll. 13 Nov. 1983 (USNM 1642707)." ;
